subject: Basketball
NCAA Basketball Tournament (Women)
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: Leading Virginia Commonwealth by 18 points in the second half, Rutgers cleared the bench to give its freshman class to play in the N.C.A.A. tournament. It nearly fumbled away the game.
